metadata.name: Love #1 by Adriane (ARW)
metadata.description:
Love #1 is Adriane's first limited edition NFT based on their mixed media work, Love #1, made of acrylic, pastels and paint pen on fine art paper. 

This piece is born from the journey of walking through the muck to a deeper magic. Adriane is on a mission to help everyone know their inner beauty and Divine recipe of love and  radiate love into the world.
